After teasing us with more cosmic themes and entities in the past The Eternals are here and audiences...don't know what to think. Currently the lowest-rated MCU film, the Eternals cinematic debut has even the most hardcore Marvel fan divided...but what do WE think of it? Join us in this recap and review of the recent polarizing entry into the MCU as we talk all things Eternals!  

